{"type":null,"faqId":16365,"title":"What can I do if my Wi-Fi connection constantly disconnects?","answer":"<p>\n</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;\">Make\n  sure you are within the working range of the Wi-Fi hotspot.</span></li>\n  <li><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">Go\n  to the Wi-Fi settings screen, touch </span><img width=\"29\" height=\"21\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141114115541979001.gif\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">&gt; </span><b style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">Advanced</b><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">, and touch </span><b style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">Keep Wi-Fi on during sleep</b><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">. From the\n  displayed option menu, choose </span><b style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">Always</b><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\n\"><br>\n</span></span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px;\">\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;\nfont-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\n\"><img width=\"141\" height=\"251\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141114115659577001.gif\"></span>\n&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\n\"><img width=\"141\" height=\"251\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141114115628258001.gif\"></span>\n<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\n\"><img width=\"141\" height=\"251\" src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=SupportImage&imagePath=/20141114115635799001.gif\"></span></span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -21.25pt;\">If the problem persists, restart Wi-Fi on your phone, and/or restart the Wi-Fi hotspot\ndevice.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 12pt; text-align: left; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\">Note: The figures are for your reference only. Actual\nscreens may vary slightly.</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 16px;\">\n<br>\n</span></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: -28.3333339691162px;\"><span style=\"fon